lead_paragraph: Kyle Okposo scored the only goal of the shootout and the New York Islanders rallied for a 2-1 victory over the Carolina Hurricanes on Tuesday night.

headline.print_headline: Okposo Gets Shootout Goal to Lift Islanders Over Hurricanes
